d9ec6dd862","tid":1820890,"uid":273059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:23:23.000Z","msg":"小英贏有大選對我地同國際都好重要<br />\n1.手足可以繼續赴台避難<br />\n2.小英親美 可以保住美國係亞太區第一島鏈既戰略部署 台灣係極之重要<br />\n3.保住香港金融中心地位 繼續捏住支那春袋 同佢玩攬炒  美國先可以繼續用香港撚支那 甚至取消關係法 直接幫佢加速支爆"},{"pid":"3c2bbe2c4653a1e9e566b7e4642211b9036fa59a","tid":1820890,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:23:35.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=634dfe06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"e6d1934131904bb72f7be1afef9beeec59b43301","tid":1820890,"uid":181436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bca5c984210954324d32723e33eb2f194121909","tid":1820890,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T19:57:00.000Z","msg":"手足，我哋冇忘記你哋。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:33:57.000Z","msg":"係 一直好擔心韓魚嬴<br />\n流亡台灣既手足就大鑊<br />\n宜家小英仲可以保住佢地<br />\n希望佢地心理健康仲可以keep住!!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地冇忘記你地!!</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fc1b65816594ff987d1c058fc6a0922d56a62f","tid":1820890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:36:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b26ce643f3e8ec43c439e2ade52760339f6dd03a","tid":1820890,"uid":135845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T21:38:16.000Z","msg":"推<i